commit dcbd71bfd72154abbc19616abcf8cd1fff6c3c63
Author: Derek Mauro <dmauro@google.com>
Date:   Mon Sep 1 06:52:33 2025 -0700

    Change absl::InlinedVector::clear() so that it does not deallocate
    any allocated space. This allows allocations to be reused and matches
    the behavior specification of std::vector::clear().

    Use shrink_to_fit() to deallocate if necessary.

    #776

    PiperOrigin-RevId: 801794564
    Change-Id: I0311e10de4eb8ec9250e8e9e2da4102982a865b3

